  }, "v12"), mdx("p", null, "D\u0129 nhi\xEAn con ng\u01B0\u1EDDi qu\xED h\u01A1n chi\xEAn nhi\u1EC1u, cho n\xEAn trong ng\xE0y Sa-b\xE1t \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c ph\xE9p l\xE0m vi\u1EC7c thi\u1EC7n.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v13"
  }, "v13"), mdx("p", null, "R\u1ED3i Ng\xE0i b\u1EA3o ng\u01B0\u1EDDi li\u1EC7t tay, \"Gi\u01A1 tay anh ra.\" Anh ta gi\u01A1 tay ra th\xEC tay \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c l\xE0nh l\u1EB7n gi\u1ED1ng nh\u01B0 tay kia. "), mdx("h6", {
