    "id": "v21"
  }, "v21"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c d\xE2n ngo\u1EA1i qu\u1ED1c s\u1EBD t\xECm \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c hi v\u1ECDng trong ng\u01B0\u1EDDi.\" Quy\u1EC1n n\u0103ng Ch\xFAa Gi\xEA-xu \u0111\u1EBFn t\u1EEB Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v22"
  }, "v22"), mdx("p", null, "L\xFAc \u1EA5y ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ta mang \u0111\u1EBFn cho Ng\xE0i m\u1ED9t ng\u01B0\u1EDDi v\u1EEBa m\xF9 v\u1EEBa c\xE2m v\xEC b\u1ECB t\xE0 ma \xE1m. Ch\xFAa Gi\xEA-xu ch\u1EEFa l\xE0nh khi\u1EBFn anh ta th\u1EA5y v\xE0 n\xF3i \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v23"
