    "id": "v24"
  }, "v24"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c ng\u01B0\u1EDDi Pha-ri-xi nghe v\u1EADy m\u1EDBi b\u1EA3o, \"\xD4ng Gi\xEA-xu ch\u1EC9 gi\u1ECFi l\u1EA5y quy\u1EC1n Sa-t\u0103ng l\xE0 ch\xFAa qu\u1EC9 m\xE0 \u0111u\u1ED5i qu\u1EC9 \u0111\xF3 th\xF4i.\" "), mdx("h6", {
