    "id": "v32"
  }, "v32"), mdx("p", null, "Ai n\xF3i ph\u1EA1m \u0111\u1EBFn Con Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi th\xEC c\xF3 th\u1EC3 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c tha nh\u01B0ng ai n\xF3i ph\u1EA1m \u0111\u1EBFn Th\xE1nh Linh s\u1EBD kh\xF4ng bao gi\u1EDD \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c tha, d\xF9 \u0111\u1EDDi n\u1EA7y cho \u0111\u1EBFn \u0111\u1EDDi sau c\u0169ng v\u1EADy.Qua l\u1EDDi n\xF3i m\xE0 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ta bi\u1EBFt c\u1EE7a c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v33"
  }, "v33"), mdx("p", null, "N\u1EBFu mu\u1ED1n c\xF3 tr\xE1i t\u1ED1t ph\u1EA3i c\xF3 c\xE2y t\u1ED1t. C\xE2y x\u1EA5u sinh tr\xE1i x\u1EA5u. Xem tr\xE1i th\xEC bi\u1EBFt c\xE2y. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v34"
  }, "v34"), mdx("p", null, "N\u1EA7y d\xF2ng d\xF5i r\u1EAFn \u0111\u1ED9c kia! C\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i v\u1ED1n \xE1c l\xE0m sao n\xF3i \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c \u0111i\u1EC1u t\u1ED1t? Mi\u1EC7ng n\xF3i ra nh\u1EEFng \u0111i\u1EC1u ch\u1EA5t ch\u1EE9a trong l\xF2ng. "), mdx("h6", {
