  }, "v35"), mdx("p", null, "Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi thi\u1EC7n ch\u1EE9a \u0111i\u1EC1u thi\u1EC7n trong l\xF2ng n\xEAn n\xF3i ra \u0111i\u1EC1u thi\u1EC7n. Nh\u01B0ng k\u1EBB \xE1c ch\u1EE9a \u0111i\u1EC1u \xE1c trong l\xF2ng n\xEAn n\xF3i ra \u0111i\u1EC1u \xE1c. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v36"
  }, "v36"), mdx("p", null, "Ta b\u1EA3o cho c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i bi\u1EBFt l\xE0 \u0111\u1EBFn Ng\xE0y X\xE9t X\u1EED ai n\u1EA5y ph\u1EA3i tr\u1EA3 l\u1EDDi v\u1EC1 nh\u1EEFng l\u1EDDi n\xF3i b\u1EEBa b\xE3i c\u1EE7a m\xECnh. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v37"
  }, "v37"), mdx("p", null, "Nh\u1EEFng l\u1EDDi c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i n\xF3i ra s\u1EBD \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c d\xF9ng \u0111\u1EC3 x\xE9t x\u1EED c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i. M\u1ED9t s\u1ED1 l\u1EDDi n\xF3i c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i s\u1EBD ch\u1EE9ng t\u1ECF c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i v\xF4 t\u1ED9i, m\u1ED9t s\u1ED1 l\u1EDDi n\xF3i s\u1EBD bu\u1ED9c t\u1ED9i c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i.\"D\xE2n ch\xFAng xin m\u1ED9t ph\xE9p l\u1EA1 "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v38"
  }, "v38"), mdx("p", null, "Sau \u0111\xF3 c\xF3 m\u1ED9t s\u1ED1 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi Pha-ri-xi v\xE0 gi\xE1o s\u01B0 lu\u1EADt th\u01B0a v\u1EDBi Ng\xE0i r\u1EB1ng, \"Th\u01B0a th\u1EA7y, ch\xFAng t\xF4i mu\u1ED1n \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c xem m\u1ED9t ph\xE9p l\u1EA1.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v39"
